_sText:
This map is a story about an abandoned base beneath the ocean on an island ... After an accident with biological weapons, an infection spread throughout the base and all workers and people who were at the bottom end up dying ... Hope you enjoy xD


======Changes made in version V2======

- Balancing entire map.

- Reduced time. 

- Light marking the buttons on the map. 

- Effects of water on the boats. 

- Power Room Door opens automatically. 

- Improvements on the map.

Errors and bugs, please contact me
